# Standardize the numerical columns

normalise_numeric = function(x) {
  if(!is.na(x) && is.numeric((x)))
    return(scale(x))
  return(x)
}

dt = dt[, lapply(.SD, normalise_numeric)] # .SD selects the subset of the dataset
